description:
After more than a decade, a new chapter in the Silent Hill franchise is on the way in the form of Silent Hill F. A brand-new mainline entry from a studio in Japan comprised of several survival-horror veterans, Silent Hill F will be the first game in the series to skip the nightmarish streets of Maine for a terrifying trip to Japan. Here's everything to know about it. 

#gaming #silenthillf
title: Silent Hill f - Everything To Know

author: GameSpot
description:
Techland's expansion turned standalone sequel winds up being the most enjoyable Dying Light so far, because it dials back the power fantasy.

It wouldn't seem to make sense to call Dying Light: The Beast a more grounded game than its predecessors. It's a game in which you routinely shift into something like X-Men's Wolverine, slashing at the undead with the ferocity of a preying mountain lion and carving them to shreds with what is basically an instant win button. But beyond the feature that informs the game's title, this expansion turned standalone sequel actually leans further into horror and survival than anything in the series, making it the most fun I've had with Dying Light to date.

#dyinglightthebeast #gaming #gamespot 

Credits: Edit Max Blumenthal, Gameplay Kurt Indovina, Tom Caswell, Jean-Luc Seipke, Written by Mark Delaney, VO by Kurt Indovina
title: Dying Light The Beast Review

ShatterRush combines fluid parkour movement and massive mechs with fully destructible environments to create flow-state combat you’ve been waiting years for!

Join over 11k players in our Open Pre-Alpha, and:

-Grapple, slide and wallrun your way to victory in a fully destructible environment.

-Battle up to 16 players online in hectic, precise combat.
Deploy towering battle mechs to (literally) level the playing field.

-Get your friends, get online and get ready to deploy into the ultimate test of movement and combat skill!
